OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally cloudy, but some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells will develop,
OL,7,Fmost likely across the southeast. A
OL,8,Ffew light afternoon showers may build
OL,9,Facross northern areas, otherwise
OL,10,Fremaining dry. Temperatures slightly
OL,11,Flower than Friday, but still very warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMost likely dry with often
OL,14,Flarge amounts of high cloud, although
OL,15,Fthere is a small chance of
OL,16,Fthunderstorms just brushing southern
OL,17,FKent as they move across the English
OL,18,FChannel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
